    {
      "type": "user-query",
      "text": "Search the web for the exact text of GDPR Article 20 (right to data portability) and find official sources that quote it. I need:\n\n1. The exact legal text of GDPR Article 20 from an official EU source\n2. Any ICO (UK Information Commissioner's Office) guidance on what \"machine-readable format\" means under Article 20\n3. Whether GDPR requires APIs or just export in a structured format\n\nReturn the exact quotes and URLs.",
