    },
    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user is asking me to search the web for specific information about GDPR Article 20. I need to find:\n1. The exact legal text of GDPR Article 20 from an official EU source\n2. ICO guidance on \"machine-readable format\" under Article 20\n3. Whether GDPR requires APIs or just export in a structured format\n\nI'll use web search to find this information. Let me start with searching for the official text of GDPR Article 20.",
      "timestamp": 1783290097073
